geico corp
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Insurance
Sub-Industry: P&C Insurance
GEICO Corporation provides property and casualty insurance services. The Company offers homeowners, fire, extended coverage, personal umbrella liability, boat owners, as well as preferred risk private passenger auto insurance. GEICO Corporation extends services throughout the United States.




